name: safety warning information
values_0_name: choking hazard. keep small parts away from children.
values_1_name: Danger of an explosion if you replace the batteries with the wrong type of battery.
values_2_name: this device and its accessories are not toys. keep them out of the reach of small children.
values_3_name: parts of this device are magnetic.
values_4_name: do not store or carry flammable or explosive materials in the same compartment as your device.
values_5_name: improper use or misuse of disposable or rechargeable batteries may cause injury or damage.
